Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請走那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝加哥駛往紐約的大陸橫跨特快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陸橫斷鐵道號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Nebular社製造的會跑的裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計上仿照了英國的皇室列車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常在後端的一等客廂設計在了前端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也是為了配合這雕刻般的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總有些趣味怪異的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別乘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有不好的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這列車被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你那第六感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有說錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有很多人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能倖存的只有運氣特別好的人和…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 只有不屬於人類的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視老婦人的不安 大陸橫斷鐵道號駛出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<1930 加利福尼亞>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這種地方幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來挖金子的 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金子就是指黃金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正是那樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們一生一世的大事業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們要從這地球上偷出金子來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球指的就是這個星球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正是那樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止 還沒有人以地球為對象進行偷盜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我們的名字會流傳千史的 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們開工吧 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開工啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<5個月後>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般大家都去河裡掏金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們在挖洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不懂的外行才會那麼干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 要是我想在海苔裡撈一點金砂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙又會說地盤什麼的 衝我發火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是恥辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我在這廢礦的前面看到了蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有著幾百條腿的大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說在東方 蜈蚣被譽為金礦之神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡說不定會出現金子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 雖然還一點都沒挖到 但太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<四個月後>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信裡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的Isaac先生及Miria小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:05:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們離開紐約已經快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但熱鬧的你們不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然十分冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且停下你們那不會有結果的掘金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我們這兒來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac先生及Miria小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直感到你們兩位就像我的親兄弟親姐妹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終都未能見到的我真正的兄弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被製造出來以前就存在著的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他們 我就覺得非常悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但多虧了Isaac先生和Miria小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能超越這份悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis的哥哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 被製造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要個弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與看起來幸福的小孩對媽媽撒嬌 讓她苦惱的事情 相類似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊 那麼 Ennis是幸福的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是Ennis的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以幫不上什麼忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 正是那樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代替 我們帶上些驚人的禮物去紐約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一分錢都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 我們去搶劫列車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 所謂搶劫列車就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐列車到達目的地後進行搶劫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再坐列車逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就像以前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幹盡壞事的黑手黨那兒把錢搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次出局 投手能把握住下一個機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是關鍵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手高舉手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是全壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾都非常感動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我們想把樂團用具放到貨物室裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不是我能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可的話 已經辦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂器是很精緻的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miria 是樂團 交響樂隊 莫扎特 保爾‧杜加斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有貝多芬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony先生 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 還是那麼有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 終於能乘上這大陸橫斷鐵道號了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼也不喜歡這列車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於年輕的你們來說 或許很愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊 Tony先生還…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑完下一個往返 我就退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟公司說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經是你們的時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是輛特殊的列車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像貨物室有巡邏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們盯上的東西似乎堆放在其他貨物室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巡邏我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dony動手的話會死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼大概啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在貨物室裡做了個隱秘房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒出大事的話應該是不會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事是指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑啊 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐上這車的一等廂 到底是怎樣的有錢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一是那黑衣樂團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白的啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和我們形成鮮明對比 感覺不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他乘客呢 有見過的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,William上議員的太太和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在報紙上看到過 不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必她們一定過著快活的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上一等車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為自己的旅途一定會平平安安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們去欣賞那些如家禽般可悲的乘客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像蛆一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著愛 帶著憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心地 小心地 把他們捻碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladd
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了列車長的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要在列車裡舉行婚禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂婚禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很熱鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是輛適合我們搶劫的列車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搶完後坐列車逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算是列車搶劫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似按計劃出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人和小姐也在車上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確認過名單了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西安置在離一等客廂最遠的列車尾端
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算出了什麼意外 我想她們也會平安無事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以中途強行停車 讓她們兩位下車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 按計劃去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是什麼更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,William議員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一出了什麼意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我妻子和女兒的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 別在這兒提那件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 傍晚來也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啊 聽說是很特別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是新型炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「或許」的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是確定的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是爆炸了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不也很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Nice 聽到炸彈也不動聲色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人聽到多不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的能偷走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那樣 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演員什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們剛才就一直在點中華料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有蜂蜜綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和他們搭話試試看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搭話試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似挺有意思的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是電影明星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能和他們搞好關係不是挺酷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼捉弄Jacuzzi了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事 Yong先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望Jacuzzi更有些社交能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次看到在臉上刺青的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化衝擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是電影明星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不是什麼電影明星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 做 酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個不良少年 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我是個很普通的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞不太明白 但突然向我們道歉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分勝負的話 是我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們贏了 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的比試啊 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦乾眼淚坐到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起吃中華料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你吃多少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛是食草的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 吃牛肉的話就是把肉和草一起吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真聰明 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了吃過東西的食物就代表你吃了那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿著帶有什麼東西的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全都變成自己的了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿著裝有很多錢的包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就既有錢又有包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東方似乎就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 你就是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花臉人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒看到這麼快樂的Jacuzzi了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacuzzi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 我完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mally
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒太失禮了 實在很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 該道歉的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家族旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我和女兒兩個人 去見我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Natalia‧William
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒叫Mally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Jacuzzi‧Splot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Isaac和Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Czeslaw‧Meyer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去紐約見家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 就像以前的Jaccuzzi一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 又不是干了壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 干了壞事會被「鐵路追蹤者」吃掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一口吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鐵路追蹤者」是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 Jacuzzi不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鐵路追蹤者」是指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤列車的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它混雜於黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點接近列車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 它能千變萬化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追上後會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 會漸漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從列車的後部開始 慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個接一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後大家都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那列車本身也會變得不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 更可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在列車內談論這事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就會來追這列車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鐵路追蹤者」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好了 會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 Jacuzzi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止「鐵路追蹤者」的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按計劃 分三組開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 關於獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說過類似的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是互相交換獲救方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 只是單純的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「鐵路追蹤者」的幽靈的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒有血緣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的只是對Hue‧Laffunate大師的忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越生死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與永生的Hue大師的最終同化是我們的誓願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要再次體會「幽靈」這個稱呼的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經不再懼怕死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們已經成為了活著的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦呢 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 我也是頭一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說過這個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從這輛列車一位年輕的乘務員那兒聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac先生 我立刻去向那位乘務員打聽獲救的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 他有點膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我剛才說出自己的真實姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacuzzi是個好人啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 一會兒問他就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這裡也有不死者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嚇唬他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊 Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅這樣嗎 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈有個偉大的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是合眾國政府逮捕了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖將其葬送於黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓偉大的主再次降臨在我們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛列車是祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客只是祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記這點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Jacuzzi 這麼慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 這列車可能會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我去一趟列車長室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的幽靈們想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把包括上議員的家人在內的乘客作為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來要求釋放首領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們偉大的Hue大師明天就要在紐約司法局接受審訊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這輛列車被選上成為死之祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我們這一行為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是與被拘禁的Hue大師的釋放以及奪回有著直接關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心點 你這小…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車要出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須去列車長室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 關鍵的獲救方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了這話的人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲救的方法根本沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}Randy和Pegour 忙著準備宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.18,0:24:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼準備宴會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是把人聚集起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喧嘩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miria 那不是準備而是宴會本身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做呢
